    <td valign="top" align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
    <b>Description:</b> <br>
    This spell will summon a Magic hitting weapon that does 6 damage and 32 delay. It is a no rent no drop which means you cannot "Trick" any newbies into buying this fine weapon. It will disapear whrn you log off.<br>
    <b>Effects:</b><br>
    Summon No Rent No Drop Weapon
    </font>
    
    </td>
